      "pause_after": 0.35
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "voice": "at-the-keeper-of-karsk-narrator",
      "text": "Tonight, the storm meant to change that.",
      "emotion": "grim",
      "tags": [],
      "exaggeration": 0.625,
      "cfg_weight": 0.38,
      "file": "lines/line-001.wav",
      "start": 5.19,
      "end": 9.71,
      "duration": 4.52,
      "pause_after": 0.5
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "speaker": "Mara",
      "voice": "at-the-keeper-of-karsk-mara",
      "text": "Bolt the door, Tomas. That wind will tear it off its hinges.",
      "emotion": "commanding",
      "tags": [],
      "exaggeration": 0.84,
      "cfg_weight": 0.344,
      "file": "lines/line-002.wav",
      "start": 10.21,
      "end": 15.41,
      "duration": 5.2,
      "pause_after": 0.3
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "speaker": "Tomas",
      "voice": "at-the-keeper-of-karsk-tomas",
      "text": "I'm trying! The latch won't hold!",
      "emotion": "panicked",
      "tags": [],
      "exaggeration": 1.0,
      "cfg_weight": 0.24,
      "file": "lines/line-003.wav",
      "start": 15.71,
      "end": 18.79,
      "duration": 3.08,
      "pause_after": 0.35
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "speaker": "Mara",
      "voice": "at-the-keeper-of-karsk-mara",
      "text": "Then lean into it, boy. With me. On three.",
      "emotion": "urgent",
      "tags": [],
      "exaggeration": 0.85,
      "cfg_weight": 0.4,
      "file": "lines/line-004.wav",
      "start": 19.14,
      "end": 23.38,
      "duration": 4.24,
      "pause_after": 0.3
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "speaker": "Tomas",
      "voice": "at-the-keeper-of-karsk-tomas",
      "text": "One... two...",
      "emotion": "breathless",
      "tags": [],
      "exaggeration": 0.875,
      "cfg_weight": 0.31,
      "file": "lines/line-005.wav",
      "start": 23.68,
      "end": 25.2,
      "duration": 1.52,
      "pause_after": 0.6
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "speaker": "Mara",
      "voice": "at-the-keeper-of-karsk-mara",
      "text": "The lamp's gone out. We light it by hand, or ships go down tonight.",
      "emotion": "grave",
      "tags": [],
      "exaggeration": 0.635,
      "cfg_weight": 0.356,
      "file": "lines/line-006.wav",
      "start": 25.8,
      "end": 30.88,
      "duration": 5.08,
      "pause_after": 0.4
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "voice": "at-the-keeper-of-karsk-narrator",
      "text": "High above them, the great glass lens waited in the dark.",
      "emotion": "hushed",
      "tags": [],
      "exaggeration": 0.35,
      "cfg_weight": 0.6,
      "file": "lines/line-007.wav",
      "start": 31.28,
      "end": 36.04,
      "duration": 4.76,
      "pause_after": 0.4
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "speaker": "Tomas",
      "voice": "at-the-keeper-of-karsk-tomas",
      "text": "I can't even see the wick.",
      "emotion": "desperate",
      "tags": [],
      "exaggeration": 1.0,
      "cfg_weight": 0.256,
      "file": "lines/line-008.wav",
      "start": 36.44,
      "end": 38.48,
      "duration": 2.04,
      "pause_after": 0.3
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "speaker": "Mara",
      "voice": "at-the-keeper-of-karsk-mara",
      "text": "You don't need to see it. You need to trust it. Strike the match.",
      "emotion": "reassuring",
      "tags": [],
      "exaggeration": 0.525,
      "cfg_weight": 0.44,
      "file": "lines/line-009.wav",
      "start": 38.78,
      "end": 43.22,
      "duration": 4.44,
      "pause_after": 0.5
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "voice": "at-the-keeper-of-karsk-narrator",
      "text": "And in that small, stubborn flame, the whole coast found its way home.",
      "emotion": "hopeful",
      "tags": [],
      "exaggeration": 0.623,
      "cfg_weight": 0.426,
      "file": "lines/line-010.wav",
